Go in there and keep your cool.
Don't get upset.

00:20:11.677 --> 00:20:14.346 line:95%,end
OK, give me a hug.
Have fun.

00:20:14.413 --> 00:20:15.847 line:95%,end
It's dance class.

00:20:15.914 --> 00:20:17.349 line:95%,end
I'm worried about Paige.

00:20:17.416 --> 00:20:20.385 line:5%,start
Her relationship with Abby is
making her a nervous wreck.

00:20:20.452 --> 00:20:22.788 line:95%,end
Look at Paige down there
practicing all by herself.

00:20:22.854 --> 00:20:25.123 line:95%,end
I don't know what my option is.

00:20:25.457 --> 00:20:28.026 line:95%,end
I said, you know,
I know you want to be here.

00:20:28.093 --> 00:20:30.229 line:95%,end
But this isn't healthy for you.

00:20:30.629 --> 00:20:33.699 line:95%,end
And she just, I want to be here
because my friends are here.

00:20:33.765 --> 00:20:35.400 line:95%,end
JILL: You know what? [interposing voices]

00:20:35.467 --> 00:20:36.668 line:95%,end
I have to get.

00:20:36.735 --> 00:20:39.371 line:95%,end
like I've come back for that
like so many times.

00:20:39.438 --> 00:20:40.806 line:95%,end
I can't do that any more.
- No.

00:20:40.906 --> 00:20:42.941 line:95%,end
- I'm like, you'll find new friends.
- No.

00:20:43.075 --> 00:20:44.710 line:95%,end
No, she won't.

00:20:44.776 --> 00:20:46.878 line:95%,end
I mean, I know she will
but these girls will always

00:20:46.945 --> 00:20:48.914 line:95%,end
be her friends.
We live so close.

00:20:48.981 --> 00:20:50.849 line:5%,start
I'm really worried about Kelly.

00:20:50.916 --> 00:20:54.152 line:5%,start
Brook and Paige and Kelly have
been through a lot with Abby

00:20:54.219 --> 00:20:56.588 line:5%,start
and I hate to see Paige so upset.

00:20:56.888 --> 00:20:57.990 line:5%,start
It kills me.

00:21:03.562 --> 00:21:06.498 line:95%,end
I want to see that face, like
that image, and it's weird.

00:21:06.565 --> 00:21:07.933 line:95%,end
It's like spooky.

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:10.736 line:95%,end
It's mystical.

00:21:11.203 --> 00:21:13.572 line:5%,start
Kendall's routine is called "Luxor."

00:21:13.705 --> 00:21:15.774 line:5%,start
And she's an Egyptian princess.

00:21:15.841 --> 00:21:18.777 line:5%,start
So it's very important to get
the arms and the hands right.

00:21:18.844 --> 00:21:20.412 line:95%,end
And Kendall is a little lazy.

00:21:20.479 --> 00:21:24.082 line:95%,end
She's letting her elbows drop and I
want to see the straight, perpendicular,

00:21:24.149 --> 00:21:25.617 line:95%,end
and parallel lines.

00:21:25.684 --> 00:21:28.320 line:95%,end
Sometimes she's great in
rehearsal and bad on stage.

00:21:28.387 --> 00:21:31.023 line:95%,end
I need Kendall to be consistent.

00:21:33.825 --> 00:21:36.328 line:95%,end
Don't dance so close to the mirrors.

00:21:37.062 --> 00:21:41.433 line:5%,start
With Chloe's sitting out this week,
this is Kendall's chance to shine.

00:21:44.803 --> 00:21:46.738 line:95%,end
Back leg higher.

00:21:46.805 --> 00:21:48.774 line:95%,end
If Kendall wins this competition,

00:21:48.840 --> 00:21:51.476 line:95%,end
then Abby will have to
give her a solo at Nationals.

00:21:51.710 --> 00:21:53.645 line:95%,end
Let's go, come on in.

00:21:57.015 --> 00:22:01.720 line:95%,end
So we're going to have the girls
are going to perform one at a time.

00:22:02.020 --> 00:22:04.823 line:95%,end
Each member of a group
should be able to do that

00:22:04.890 --> 00:22:07.526 line:95%,end
group routine choreography like a soloist.

00:22:07.826 --> 00:22:10.529 line:95%,end
When they do it
one at a time by themselves,

00:22:11.196 --> 00:22:15.600 line:95%,end
it gives us the opportunity to see
who's using the wrong arms on a turn

00:22:15.667 --> 00:22:18.136 line:95%,end
or who's turning one more time
than everybody else.

00:22:18.203 --> 00:22:19.671 line:95%,end
Are we ready to go?

00:22:30.349 --> 00:22:32.050 line:95%,end
Kendall's on.

00:22:33.018 --> 00:22:34.519 line:95%,end
Come on, tighten up.

00:22:36.988 --> 00:22:38.957 line:5%,start
I wish Ricky could teach
the group rehearsal

00:22:39.024 --> 00:22:42.461 line:5%,start
because he gives you nice critiques,
not screaming at you.

00:22:43.128 --> 00:22:45.397 line:95%,end
ABBY: Face, face, face!
Come on!

